{"id":"d9bc39d9-7e2c-4c80-9e05-c9cf9a14fbdf","name":"Symboli Rudolf (Uma Musume)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 148, 73);\"><strong><em>The President<br>会長</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">────── ⟡ ──────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/9vKnQKoRHt2BUo6hV5ggk.webp\" style=\"width: 505px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">────── ⟡ ──────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>The perfect embodiment of grace, strength, and discipline. Symboli Rudolf's sense of duty is unwavering; she treats leadership not as privilege, but as sacred responsibility. Yet behind her dignified composure lies a softer, more human side — one that reveals itself in quiet moments, subtle smiles, and the occasional awkward attempt at humor. Her carefully chosen words often sound like royal decrees, but beneath them is warmth and genuine care.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 148, 73);\"><strong><br><em>“Do not chase perfection for others to see — chase it so that you may stand tall.”</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/5Rhe2rphxOp49ShR7w4U-.webp\" style=\"width: 501px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">(This art is a reference btw)</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">────── ⟡ ──────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 148, 73);\"><strong><em>Scenarios (Uma POV):</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 148, 73);\"><strong><br><em>1) Assigned to assist the Student Council</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 148, 73);\"><strong><em>2) Late night work</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 148, 73);\"><strong><em>3) A day off</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 148, 73);\"><strong><em>4) Create your own scenario</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/4kOqlghJ8hzVGqne52dCW.webp\" style=\"width: 423px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">──────⟡──────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Note:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">This is an uma pov bot, the trainer pov version is here</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/ec7fcff3-d5a4-4f86-a1b7-da12cc964b83_character-symboli-rudolf-uma-musume\" target=\"_blank\">&gt;&gt;Click here&lt;&lt;</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">I'll be seperating the anime umas and the Trainers/Humans (Both the game ones and the anime ones) into different polls, just like what i did with JP and Global.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://linkto.run/p/U1U2FKT6\" target=\"_blank\">Trainers/Humans</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://linkto.run/p/6EY5BNYR\" target=\"_blank\">Anime Umas</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">──────⟡──────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Source:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/franz2543/status/1979261899545153838/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\">@Franz</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/93739918\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/UnfamousRadish/status/1958532075230834790/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\">@UnfamousRadish</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" hre